After completing the setup steps and starting both the frontend and backend servers, the application becomes fully functional.
The system offers two types of users: Employee and Manager, each with dedicated features.

Employee Capabilities

Log in using provided credentials

Mark daily attendance (once per day)

View personal profile information

Manager Capabilities

Log in using manager credentials

View attendance records of all employees

Monitor daily activity and attendance status

All operations are backed by secure JWT authentication, clean API architecture, and responsive UI components.